# CI Workflows

- [github/workflows/install-e2e.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/install-e2e.yml)
  - Purpose: Runs end-to-end install/setup tests (`scripts/test-install.sh`).
  - Trigger: Only on GitHub Releases (`release` with `types: [published]`).
  - Requires `GITHUB_TOKEN` (set as `secrets.UMF_TOKEN`) for private/API tarball downloads.

